Subject: The Continuing Penguicon Robot Build
Description: Come help design and build a robot during the convention. Donations may be accepted depending on the robot design. No skill necessary to help but prior experience would be useful. Useful skills include familiarity with micro-controllers, structural design, costume design, programming, graphic design, and logic!  Speakers include:James Hice, John D. Bell - Track: DIY, Tech  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
